  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Cloud Engineer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Company’s Profile:</strong></p>\n<p>Our client is an international technology and engineering company that specialises in providing innovative digital and security solutions to their esteemed clients. They are looking out for <u><strong>Cloud Engineers</strong></u> to join their team and contribute to their ongoing success.</p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Plan, execute, and oversee technical aspects of projects</li>\n  <li>Lead or support new system/network setups and upgrades</li>\n  <li>Ensure operational systems meet Service Level Agreements (SLAs)</li>\n  <li>Perform routine maintenance and operational tasks efficiently</li>\n  <li>Troubleshoot and resolve technical issues</li>\n  <li>Maintain clear project documentation and reporting</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience with Windows Server and Linux in virtual environments</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of virtualization, hypervisors, and Nutanix platforms (a plus)</li>\n  <li>Familiarity with VPNs, firewalls, switches, and routers</li>\n  <li>Strong communication skills for both technical and non-technical audiences</li>\n  <li>Proactive mindset with strong analytical and conceptual thinking</li>\n  <li>Team player with the ability to work independently and excellent interpersonal skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>(EA Reg No: 20C0312)</p>\n<p>Please email a copy of your detailed resume to <strong>qianyu@talentsis.com.sg</strong> for immediate processing.</p>\n<p>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
